{"tid":1561340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多區市民大合唱　淘大有男子對唱国歌被打","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:26:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6354f3eef35add6371b2ed841210b9781a7b0b72","tid":1561340,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"修訂《逃犯條例》引致風波未平。有網民今晚(11日)約8時許相繼於全港多區發起在商場大合唱，包括有西環西寶城、淘大花園商場、荷里活廣場、沙田新城市廣場、香港仔廣場、奧海城二期等。<br />\n<br />\n晚上約7時許，淘大花園有近百人聚集，期間有一名男子攜同三名小童，高唱國歌，被現場人士圍堵並引發衝突，男子被打傷面部流血，報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市廣場有約3000名市民聚集於中庭合唱，廣場附近的百步梯約晚上8時，有人宣讀示威期間死去的人士之名字，呼籲現場人士開手機電筒默哀3分鐘。西環西寶城有約300名人士聚集，有人帶備大聲公播歌，同時有人派發歌詞單張。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣廣場有近200名市民聚集，現場有人悼念18年前在9月11日於美國恐襲的死者，又在商場三樓掛上兩條直幡，包括「五大訴求、缺一不可」及「荃民葵手、捍衞我城」。香港仔廣場有約400人聚集。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190911/mobile/bkn-20190911201723258-0911_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2e2aab39a1e9611081c86f53038aca4e46fbf26e","tid":1561340,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"15585e434f433ab13335a307458c47e07bf64171","tid":1561340,"uid":314980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"其實點解會開拖？"},{"pid":"f4a262c1fd258f6ccabc9988752dd40479e9b879","tid":1561340,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愛国男打人先</span></span>"},{"pid":"196b822c57d4a9c52eaa41ae70e2791702f03794","tid":1561340,"uid":264369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"建議為區選選區，尤其反自動當選的，各區獨立設一個台<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 既然冇大台提供可靠懶人包結論，就要期望唔少唔多喜歡睇文字的手足認真閱讀分析 &quot;raw material&quot; ．每台只處理跟各人相關的資料，可以方便大家作出明智決定，亦方便 admin 管理（移動錯台post／垃圾文 etc）<br />\n2. 早兩天有關 歐頌賢 及 任嘉兒 的討論，大家要跟post都已經有Ｄ難度，遲下區多人多時間逼，再加大大班臥底時，肯定亂到九彩，早日作好安排好Ｄ．"},{"pid":"d3acc19e633681883c04eda9e5d26fb9455f3d43","tid":1561340,"uid":271234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"46f6f2c9bbc2075bfbafd442f1dc313ff5fef9f5","tid":1561340,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edu5dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edu5dD.png&h=f7e4a997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d8150623bbf012c1f29a6505b8379c3c2c53659","tid":1561340,"uid":156527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"打得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0567cb66c57522121bcfe4615070c70713b8421d","tid":1561340,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim